CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1784485125
OL,3,CWhat will be Sir Keir Starmer's legacy
OL,4,Cfor Scotland?
OL,6,FSir Keir's decision to replace Ian
OL,7,FMurray with Mr Alexander as Scottish
OL,8,FSecretary also changed the tone of how
OL,9,Fgovernments in Westminster and
OL,10,FHolyrood would interact in the run up
OL,11,Fto May's vote.
OL,13,F"They wanted Douglas in because he is
OL,14,Fmuch more robust with the SNP but Ian
OL,15,Fwas sent in to reset the relationship
OL,16,F(with the Scottish Government) by No10
OL,17,Fand the prime minister," said a
OL,18,FWhitehall source.
OL,26,@xD@ApmxD@^pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G21/24
