OL,3,CWhat will be Sir Keir Starmer's legacy
OL,4,Cfor Scotland?
OL,6,FSupporters of the decision said Mr
OL,7,FAlexander ensured there was greater
OL,8,Fpublic impact for decisions made by
OL,9,Fthe UK Government in Scotland.
OL,11,FRegardless of which approach was best,
OL,12,Fthe contrast in approaches is another
OL,13,Fsign that people were unsure of the
OL,14,Fprime minister's overarching vision, a
OL,15,Fproblem that extended beyond the
OL,16,FHolyrood election campaign.
OL,18,F"Maybe the problem wasn't a Scottish
OL,19,Fthing," said a Scottish Labour source.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G22/24
