OL,3,CWhat will be Sir Keir Starmer's legacy
OL,4,Cfor Scotland?
OL,6,F"You need to tell a story to all of
OL,7,Fthe country and tailor it to Scotland
OL,8,Fand if you don't have the first part
OL,9,Fyou can't have the second."
OL,11,FOr as another Scottish Labour figure
OL,12,Fput it more bluntly: "I feel a bit
OL,13,Fsorry for him because I don't think he
OL,14,Fdeserved what happened to him.
OL,16,F"But a lot of it was brought on
OL,17,Fhimself by him and his team."
